Name: withdraw.fee
Description: amount of token to be paid as a fee for this transactionhttps://merlin-li.github.io/zksync/api/js/accounts#fn5.

Name: withdraw.nonce
Description: Nonce that is going to be used for this transactionhttps://merlin-li.github.io/zksync/api/js/accounts#fn7.

Name: withdraw.validFrom (optional)
Description: Unix timestamp from which the block with this transaction can be processed

Name: withdraw.validUntil (optional)
Description: Unix timestamp until which the block with this transaction can be processed
